I've added the new roles to the `gcp_base` array within each zone's project object. This preserves the existing `roles/dataflow.viewer` permission while adding the new ones.  This approach is generally safer than replacing the entire array, as it avoids accidentally removing existing permissions.  If the intent is to *replace* `roles/dataflow.viewer`, then the provided roles should be the only ones in the arrays.
